{"tid":747402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[精算系]世界盃美斯牙朗表現評估(含分析)","createTime":"2018-07-18T10:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T09:07:47.000Z","uid":163207,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40f4d2e73ca51971a48e33548dc639973cc14b9e","tid":747402,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"首先入球/助攻各計1分,然後因應對手最後排名得出系數再相乘,避免對廢隊刷數據<br />\n<br />\n系數如下:<br />\n小組出局1分<br />\n16強2分<br />\n8強3分<br />\n4強4分<br />\n亞軍5分<br />\n冠軍6分<br />\n<br />\n美斯: 1球(尼日利亞,小組賽) +2助攻(法國,冠軍)=1x1+2x6=13分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牙朗: 3球(西班牙,16強)+1球(摩洛哥,小組賽)=3x2+1x1=7分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牙傾:2球(突尼西亞,小組)+3球(巴拿馬,小組)+1球(哥比倫亞,16強)=2x1+3x1+1x2=7分"},{"pid":"eeb14dee66ffb6a8fb9d4f7f805a02ec09022732","tid":747402,"uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"有興趣嘅朋友可以根據公式計算你心水球員今屆嘅表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ccf7853a33ffc680b0b35c8a2cd151a8185b88","tid":747402,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5feef65f6ae820dcbdacf7dfe17af3d2555f2bf","tid":747402,"uid":58811,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"大佬你吹奏得有d質素好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509b7d1a1ee2cf21bd2d571be6e1894dd4ba8e48","tid":747402,"uid":149955,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"個計法好噁心，偏心到出面，直接寫感情分美斯滿分算啦<br />\n<br />\n洗咩辛9苦自己扮中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c2e95d10f75a8960bfbabe30d439ad699600e3","tid":747402,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply